en_5621805_1	Police said that the motorcyclist had travelled towards Galle in the lane meant for highway authorities to travel towards Colombo.
en_5621805_2	According to police the motorcyclist had traveled about two kilometers towards Galle when it collided with an oncoming van that was travelling towards Colombo.
